object.Alien Dawg.name: Alien Dawg
object.Alien Dawg.description: An indica that has a light, bitter taste but a contrasting sour and pungent ordor.
object.Alien Kush.name: Alien Kush
object.Alien Kush.description: A hardy plant with a taste reminiscent of tea and a smell reminiscent of pine.
object.Big Bud.name: Big Bud
object.Big Bud.description: An old favorite of the Ferngill Republic. This strain now finds prosperity in the Gotoro Empire.
object.Chemdawg.name: Chemdawg
object.Chemdawg.description: Chemdawg or Chemdog, it doesn't matter. Not for cannabis newbies.
object.Fruity Pebbles OG.name: Fruity Pebbles OG
object.Fruity Pebbles OG.description: How did you manage to get your hands on some seeds?
object.Granddaddy Purple.name: Granddaddy Purple
object.Granddaddy Purple.description: This staple inherits a grape and verry aroma. You can use it to create Fruit Pebbles OG.
object.Green Ribbon.name: Green Ribbon
object.Green Ribbon.description: A subtle strain that lends itself to an earthy taste. You can use it to create Fruit Pebbles OG.
object.Las Vegas Purple Kush.name: Las Vegas Purple Kush
object.Las Vegas Purple Kush.description: LVPK for short. A wonderful indica-dominant hybrid that combines the best of both sativas and indicas.
object.Purple Urkle.name: Purple Urkle
object.Purple Urkle.description: An indica with a complex flavore palate with a blend of skunk, berry, and fresh grapes.
object.Tahoe Alien.name: Tahoe Alien
object.Tahoe Alien.description: A strain that inherits a subtle earthy aroma with hints of lemon and pine. You can use it to create Fruit Pebbles OG.
object.White Rhino.name: White Rhino
object.White Rhino.description: A hybrid of White Widow and an unknown strain, this indica is a popular choice those those looking for relaxation and symptom relief.
object.Alien Dawg Starter.name: Alien Dawg Starter
object.Alien Dawg Starter.description: Plant these in the summer. Takes 13 days to mature, afterwards it continues to produce every 3 days.
